  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE WAVES OF DEADLY SLIMES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/4d253c2690cf1e401954ebed5140b126.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/4d253c2690cf1e401954ebed5140b126.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/4d253c2690cf1e401954ebed5140b126.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Slime Squisher, your main goal is to protect a strawberry by squishing  slimes with your cursor. The slimes come in a variety of sizes and shapes. Some are fast, some are slow, some shoot bullets, and some are big and bulky!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COLLECT COINS AND PURCHASE UPGRADES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/b040e1141e22fc41d6895e19d77cdf31.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/b040e1141e22fc41d6895e19d77cdf31.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/b040e1141e22fc41d6895e19d77cdf31.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slimes have a small chance to drop gold coins. These coins can be spent on permanent upgrades which will make you more powerful on your next run!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLEASH CHAOS ONTO THE SLIMES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/96f46509199d55a423a512df04953d87.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/96f46509199d55a423a512df04953d87.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/96f46509199d55a423a512df04953d87.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your strawberry at all cost! With each wave, you’ll grow stronger and eventually  unleash total chaos onto the slimes!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/cc65b510cb28d9a634680d0a8b0bb441.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/cc65b510cb28d9a634680d0a8b0bb441.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/cc65b510cb28d9a634680d0a8b0bb441.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slime Squisher has a variety of different gamemodes to be played, some are more challenging than others. Create your own build by combining different upgrades.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regular gamemode: Easy, normal and hard difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meta progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Active abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And a lot of squished slimes!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE WAVES OF DEADLY SLIMES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/4d253c2690cf1e401954ebed5140b126.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/4d253c2690cf1e401954ebed5140b126.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/4d253c2690cf1e401954ebed5140b126.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Slime Squisher, your main goal is to protect a strawberry by squishing  slimes with your cursor. The slimes come in a variety of sizes and shapes. Some are fast, some are slow, some shoot bullets, and some are big and bulky!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COLLECT COINS AND PURCHASE UPGRADES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/b040e1141e22fc41d6895e19d77cdf31.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/b040e1141e22fc41d6895e19d77cdf31.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/b040e1141e22fc41d6895e19d77cdf31.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slimes have a small chance to drop gold coins. These coins can be spent on permanent upgrades which will make you more powerful on your next run!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLEASH CHAOS ONTO THE SLIMES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/96f46509199d55a423a512df04953d87.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/96f46509199d55a423a512df04953d87.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/96f46509199d55a423a512df04953d87.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect your strawberry at all cost! With each wave, you’ll grow stronger and eventually  unleash total chaos onto the slimes!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/cc65b510cb28d9a634680d0a8b0bb441.poster.avif?t=1754489175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/cc65b510cb28d9a634680d0a8b0bb441.webm?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449900/extras/cc65b510cb28d9a634680d0a8b0bb441.mp4?t=1754489175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slime Squisher has a variety of different gamemodes to be played, some are more challenging than others. Create your own build by combining different upgrades.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regular gamemode: Easy, normal and hard difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meta progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Active abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And a lot of squished slimes!</p></li></ul>",
